2. [P1] Error handling bypasses i18n and leaks raw transport text. [testpage.jsx](/C:/Dev/menuapp-code-review/pages/TestPage/base/testpage.jsx#L14) throws `HTTP ${res.status}` and [testpage.jsx](/C:/Dev/menuapp-code-review/pages/TestPage/base/testpage.jsx#L21) stores `err.message`, so users see raw English/browser strings that do not translate or update on language change. FIX: store error keys or structured error codes and render via `t(...)`.

